🏗 Engineering Highlights

This project demonstrates strong understanding of:

Go slices and mutation patterns

Regex-based parsing strategies

Stateful token processing

CLI application architecture

Unit-driven development

Clean separation of concerns

The punctuation engine was carefully designed to properly handle ellipsis without corrupting token spacing — a common edge case in text processors.

